    Do not filter out duplicate subscriptions on the XSUB side of
    XSUB/XPUB, so that ZMQ_XPUB_VERBOSE doesn't get blocked by forwarding
    devices (as long as the devices all use ZMQ_XPUB_VERBOSE)

