commit 12486fecc4f8d9a3bed37cf3d732b1250b075e24
Author: Martin Sustrik <sustrik@250bpm.com>
Date:   Fri Feb 18 17:57:59 2011 +0100

    Fix MSVC and SunStudio builds with OpenPGM
    
